MBOMBELA &#8211; A man and a woman were killed in an horrific accident at the traffic lights near Nelsville, on the N4 on Saturday. According to Netcare911 spokesman, Ms Athlenda Mathe, three others, including two minors, were also injured after a Ford Ranger and a Toyota Tazz collided. Mathe said the male driver of the Tazz died on the scene and his female passenger later in hospital.